SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c05068681
Version: 2

HPSBGN03569 rev.2 - HPE OneView for VMware vCenter (OV4VC), Remote Disclosure
of Information

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2016-04-04
Last Updated: 2016-04-06

Potential Security Impact: Remote Disclosure of Sensitive Information

Source: Hewlett Packard Enterprise, Product Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
Potential security vulnerabilities have been identified in the server running
HP OneView for VMware vCenter (OV4VC) version 7.8.1 or earlier. The
vulnerabilities may lead to remote disclosure of information.

References:

CVE-2014-3566
CVE-2016-0800
CVE-2016-0705
CVE-2016-0799
CVE-2016-2842
PSRT110069

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HPE Oneview for VMware vCenter 7.8.1 and earlier releases

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2014-3566    (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:P/I:N/A:N)        4.3
CVE-2016-0800    (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:P/I:N/A:N)        4.3
CVE-2016-0705    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)       10.0
CVE-2016-0799    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)       10.0
CVE-2016-2842    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)       10.0
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HPE has provided the following software update to resolve this vulnerability:
HP OneView for VMware vCenter 7.8.2.

The update is available from HPE Software Depot: https://h20392.www2.hpe.com/
portal/swdepot/displayProductInfo.do?productNumber=HPVPR

Note: HPE recommends customers using OV4VC 7.8.1 and earlier should upgrade
to OV4VC 7.8.2. This addresses all SSL security vulnerabilities reported
through March 28, 2016.

HISTORY
Version:1 (rev.1) - 4 April 2016 Initial release
Version:2 (rev.2) - 6 April 2016 corrected typo in resolution URL

